            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>diced onion</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 3-5 min or until softened</p><p>Once softened, add your<strong> ginger paste</strong>, <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and <strong>curry powder</strong> and cook for a further 1 min</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
